FANTASY UPDATE:
This is a fantasy update for all you members who have been requesting more storline/themed shoots! Enjoy
At an all girls academy it can be hard to fit in, especially if you are the new girl. When Leilani start academy in a different town she desperately wants to get in with the cool gang and will do whatever it takes to be one of them, even if it means getting shocked, slapped, and fucked in the bathroom after class!
title: The New Girl
